data.name: 28VCK
data.description:
The key to future healthcare is the realization of personalized and predictive healthcare based on data.
The 28VC blockchain can effectively record and manage dental health information using its own development technology. This is impossible to modify and possibility of personal information leakage can be reduced. So, we are confident that we will be able to help make healthcare innovation a reality. 
The next generation implant, 'triplant' is combine with this new blockchain technology to utilize and database users' dental information. In addition, through the linkage of the health care industry, it will be used in various ways by dividing it into data, platform, and device.
The next generation of living implants, 'triplant' which were jointly researched and developed by Korea and Japan, has a database that has been tested on animals for decades to prove that there is no problem with the implant.
Since January 21, we have a database for people through support for clinical trials We are focusing on clinical research and development with the goal of commercialization in the second half of 22.
Currently, we are planning to conduct clinical trials and clinical research among cooperative organizations in both Korea and Japan.
